==English==

===Etymology===
By pejorative reference to a advertisement by the Swift Boat Veterans for Truth during the 2004 United States presidential election campaign.

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# {{US|politics|pejorative}} To [[attack]] a [[politician]] with [[specious]] claims.

====Usage notes====
* As the term's origin is still widely recognized, it is generally used only by those who consider the original advertisement to have been a specious attack, and use of this term is likely to be interpreted as an indication that one holds this view.

